w\u00f6rungstheoretische Diskurse im Feld der Alternativmedizin und Esoterik im Online- und Offline-Raum anhand anschaulicher Beispiele beleuchtet. <br/>Das Buch nimmt Sie mit in die verflochtenen Gefilde der Hom\u00f6opathie und Alternativmedizin, Impfgegner_innen und Geistheiler_innen, Anthroposophie, dem Glauben an Chemtrails, \u00fcber antisemitische Verschw\u00f6rungstheorien und der v\u00f6lkischen Anastasia-Bewegung bis hin zu Reichsb\u00fcrgerideologie und Brauner Esoterik.", "language": null, "image": "https://img2.libreriauniversitaria.it/EIT/280/257/9783961462575.jpg", "pagetype": "product", "links": ["https://www.libreriauniversitaria.it", "https://www.chegiochi.it", "https://www.primainfanzia.it", "https://www.madeincucina.com", "https://www.webster.it", "https://www.libreriascolastica.it", "/BIT/page_libri.htm", "/page_libri_di_testo.htm", "/page_libri_scolastici.htm", "/page_ebook.htm", "/page_libri-lingua-straniera.htm", "/page_cartoleria.htm", "/page_test_universitari.htm", "/page_ammissione-tesi.htm", "https://edizioni.libreriauniversitaria.it/", "https://www.webster.it/page_dvd.htm", "https://www.webster.it/page_videogames.htm", "https://www.webster.it/page_musica.htm", "https://www.chegiochi.it", "/aiuto_buoni-regalo.htm", "/aiuto_18app.htm", "/aiuto_cartadeldocente.htm", "/page_libri.htm", "/page_libri.htm", "/libri/classifica-piu-venduti.htm", "/page_libri_piu_venduti_italia.htm", "/page_remainders.htm", "/page_promozioni.htm", "/page_prossime_uscite.htm", "/page_audiolibri.htm", "/page_top_libri_2022.htm", "/page_premi_letterari.htm", "http://www.paperback.it", "/page_reparti_libri.htm", "/page_ebook.htm", "/page_ebook.htm", "/ebook/italiano/classifica-ebook-piu-venduti.htm", "/page_ebook_guida.htm", "http://www.paperback.it", "/page_ammissione-tesi.htm", "/page_ammissione-tesi.htm", "/page_pubblica_tesi.htm", "/page_guide_tesi.htm", "/page_come_scrivere_una_tesi.htm", "/page_test_universitari.htm", "/page_test_studentpass.htm", "/page_test_am